.TH CGWATCHERD 8 "November 2025" "0.1.0" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
cgwatcherd \- Daemon to monitor cgroup memory usage and notify users
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cgwatcherd
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cgwatcherd
runs in the background and monitors cgroups. It sends desktop notifications when a cgroup exceeds configured memory usage thresholds.
.SH CONFIGURATION
Configuration is stored in \fI~/.config/cgwatch/cgwatcherd.ini\fR.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR cgwatcher (1)